These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse, cat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, daisy
1. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
3. the person who growslily is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
5. the person who growssunflower is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Pet   | cat | turtle | mouse |
| Flower    | sunflower    | daisy | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, balloon-flower
3 different pets are kept: goat, bird, dog
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the owner of the bird is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower       | tulip | balloon-flower | daffodil |
| Pet   | dog    | bird     | goat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different games are played: domino, scrabble, snooker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, aristoff
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Game         | snooker     | scrabble | domino |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | old-henry     | aristoff  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, photography, board-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, dancer, paramedic
1. the person who's hobby is photography is the dancer##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the paramedic##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Hobby   | board-games | photography  | cooking  |
| Job         | lawyer  | dancer | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, punk, folk
1. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of pop##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage         | soy-milk   | mirinda | hot-chocolate    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | folk     | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, ship
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat, horse
1. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the horse is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Transport   | skateboard | ship | taxi   |
| Pet   | horse     | hedgehog    | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
City: london, marseilles, hannover
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, surfing
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to london is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person traveling to hannover##2
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| City   | hannover | london | marseilles |
| Sport           | golf         | snowboarding         | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, scientist, pilot
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, montecristo, ritmeester
1. the dunhill-smoker is between the montecristo-smoker and the electrician##2
2. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Job   | scientist | pilot | electrician |
| Cigar    | montecristo    | dunhill | ritmeester     |

