.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different games are played: canasta, chess, scrabble
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Game   | scrabble   | chess  | canasta  |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | musical | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, singing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, time-travel, satire
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Hobby   | traveling    | singing      | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel | satire | animation   |

