2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Hobby         | writing | drawing | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | skiing | surfing   | weightlifting |

