.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, taxi, bike
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Transport          | bike | trike | taxi  |
| Birthday   | january      | december  | april |

