.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, scooter
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, grapefruit, carrot
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | helicopter | scooter | trike    |
| Food           | grapefruit     | carrot  | kiwi |

