.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
City: rome, colone, san-francisco
There 3 different types of food: corn, potato, kiwi
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person eating potato##1
4. the person eating corn is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| City         | san-francisco | rome   | colone |
| Food   | potato   | corn | kiwi      |

