2. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | r&b | punk | dubstep |
| City   | prague   | san-francisco          | marseilles |

