.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
House: craftsman, palace, townhouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| House     | palace  | townhouse   | craftsman |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster | satire       |

 